<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My GitHub Actions Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello World!</h1>
    <p>这个页面是由 GitHub Actions 自动部署的。</p>
    <p>部署时间: <span id="time"></span></p>
    <script>
        document.getElementById('time').innerHTML = new Date().toLocaleString();
    </script>
</body>
</html>